don't like to get out that much.

10:24.520 --> 10:25.885
I suppose so.

10:27.760 --> 10:29.046
Are you... Uh...

10:29.320 --> 10:30.810
What is that? Um...

10:31.160 --> 10:32.605
Agoraphobia?

