coming from the apartment?

11:23.760 --> 11:26.843
No strange sounds last
night when she died?

11:26.920 --> 11:29.969
Since I don't know when
she died, day or night,

11:30.040 --> 11:32.361
and since I've already
made it clear

11:32.440 --> 11:37.367
that I didn't hear anything out of the
ordinary coming from her apartment,

11:38.240 --> 11:41.323
then I'd venture to guess
that we are entering

11:42.200 --> 11:45.090
into an area of...
Hmm, redundancy?

11:48.000 --> 11:49.286
Okay, now we're done.

11:49.360 --> 11:52.170
Thank you for the coffee.
I'm gonna give you a couple of cards.

11:52.440 --> 11:56.490
If you think of
anything, uh, call me.

11:57.080 --> 11:58.684
Thank you.I will.

12:01.920 --> 12:02.921
Okay.

12:06.000 --> 12:07.729
Hey, this is a really nice vase.

12:07.800 --> 12:10.167
It's a little confusing,
but it's nice.

12:10.240 --> 12:12.322
I'm sure you could
figure it out.

