<i>Her name is Justine Waters,</i>

12:52.960 --> 12:55.201
<i>"and she was known as
“America's little darling. "</i>

12:55.320 --> 12:57.084
<i>The sole heiress of
the Waters fortune,</i>

12:57.160 --> 12:59.606
<i>estimated in the hundreds
of millions of dollars,</i>

