<i>At the time, she held the world
record of 14 straight hours.</i>

13:15.560 --> 13:18.291
<i>Now, there's been much speculation
on Justine's whereabouts.</i>

13:18.360 --> 13:21.125
<i>Theories range from her running
off with a Saudi prince</i>

13:21.200 --> 13:23.009
<i>to her being a victim
