13:23.440 --> 13:25.488
<i>Now while the great and
powerful Phillip Waters</i>

13:25.560 --> 13:27.483
<i>claimed until his
death five years ago</i>

13:27.560 --> 13:29.449
<i>that he never stopped
looking for his daughter,</i>

13:30.360 --> 13:32.681
<i>Justine's 17-year silence</i>

13:32.760 --> 13:36.048
<i>remains the most talked about
missing persons mystery to date.</i>

13:36.680 --> 13:39.968
<i>In the days leading up to what would
become her historic vanishing act,</i>

13:40.280 --> 13:42.681
<i>it was rumored that
18-year-old Justine Waters</i>

13:42.760 --> 13:46.845
<i>had just become engaged to Prince
