Interesting. Yeah? Why is that?

14:05.040 --> 14:07.884
Well, this could
be a family crest.

14:08.480 --> 14:10.482
This is the letter "M," correct?

14:10.560 --> 14:13.006
Well, that was the intention.
The drawing is rough, but...

14:13.080 --> 14:15.048
Well, where'd you find this?

14:15.120 --> 14:18.329
I can't really tell you.
