14:18.840 --> 14:20.808
Okay. I got a book in the back,

14:20.880 --> 14:22.769
something of an
almanac, so to speak.

14:22.840 --> 14:24.410
Might be able to find a match.

14:24.640 --> 14:26.722
How long do you think...
